  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13099593/jungfraubahn-ski-train.jpg" alt="Ski Train" data-udi="umb://media/e4dbc89ec44546d3bea78bddbbbb6946" /></p>
<h2>Reach resort by rail</h2>
<p>Thinking of travelling by train this winter to some of Europe's best loved resorts? Then jump on board with an Inghams ski holiday by train.</p>
<p>From train tracks to ski tracks, step off and ski on. Enjoy stress-free travel, flexible luggage allowance and room to stretch out. Leave the planning to us and enjoy the journey.</p>
<p><strong>Why travel by train? </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Stress free travel</li>
<li>Shorter check in times - 90 mins prior to departure</li>
<li>Whilst on board - freedom to move around, more space</li>
<li>Luggage allowance - more allowance than flying at no extra charge</li>
<li>Beautiful scenery along the way</li>
<li>Doing your bit for the planet by travelling by train instead of plane</li>
</ul>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/5e51e91275d64f7d9c63753bbf5ae0d3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5e51e91275d64f7d9c63753bbf5ae0d3}" title="From London St. Pancras" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="">All train travel deals</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Our ski holidays by train</h2>
<p>Next stop? A ski holiday of a lifetime. Experience an effortless journey when you travel by train to these popular ski resorts. See all the countries and their resorts that you can reach by train for your winter holiday below.</p>
<p>All trains will depart from St Pancras train station in London and will get you as close to your resort as possible via train, we will then arrange either coach or car hire to get you to your resort, all included in the package price.</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow " style="text-align: center;">
