<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2>Eurostar snow train package to France</h2>
<p>The Eurostar snow train is back again for winter 2024/25, taking passengers from London St Pancras International Station on to French resorts - Val D ’Isere, Tignes and Les Arcs. With both Standard and Premier Classes on the Eurostar, comfort and choice are guaranteed all the way.</p>
<p><strong>The Eurostar snow train</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Running from the 21st December 2024 to the 22nd February 2025</li>
<li>Outbound: Saturdays from St Pancras - Bourg St Maurice at 09:01-17:45</li>
<li>Inbound: Sundays from Bourg St Maurice - London St Pancras at 08:09 - 15:57</li>
<li>Includes just one stop in Lille, France.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Why book the Inghams Eurostar snow train package –</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>You get an extra day of skiing – The Eurostar snow train departs London on Saturdays and returns on the following Sunday, meaning you have 7 full days on the slopes.</li>
<li>We give you 7 days for the price of 6 - an extra night of accommodation is provided in Bourg St Maurice on the Saturday evening before return train journey, plus when you buy a 6 day lift pass and ski hire, we will cover the cost for your 7th day.</li>
<li>Our packages include train travel, transfers and your choice of accommodation in the popular resorts of <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val D ’Isere</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a>.</li>
<li>On average, the train is around 3 hours quicker than usual train options due to only one platform change in Lille.</li>
<li>On the Eurostar you can stay connected with free Wi-Fi.</li>
<li>Indulge in onboard refreshments.</li>
<li>Make the most of the generous luggage allowance.</li>
</ul>
<p>Read more about the Eurostar Snow Train - <a data-udi="umb://document/2bf29261e6e747a98423e8b40c1d21ea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2bf29261e6e747a98423e8b40c1d21ea}" title="Eurostar Snow Train">view our Guide</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
