<h2><img style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13099193/eurostar-snow-6-838x300.jpg" alt="traintravel" data-udi="umb://media/757d05a8878648b6bff47483a20636cc" /></h2>
<h2>Be part of the change:</h2>
<p>The places you visit as part of your Inghams holiday are special, and it’s our responsibility to keep them that way, long into the future. Switching the plane for a train can reduce the carbon footprint of your holiday considerably. We want to make it as easy as possible for our customers to take the train, so we are offering rail travel to 3 countries across Europe. </p>
<ul>
<li>We’ve committed to reducing our carbon by 50% by 2030 - 59% of holiday currently comes from flights.</li>
<li>Flying is the fastest growing source of greenhouse gas emissions in Europe.</li>
<li>By traveling by rail our customers can connect with the changing landscapes as they travel to their destination</li>
</ul>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72" href="/{localLink:umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72}" class="c-btn">Sustainability with Inghams</a></p>
